oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mountain girl with guitar
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Mountain girl singer at broadcast over WSM of the Square Dance at McMinnville, Warren County, Tennessee. She is seated and holding her guitar.
WSM's first official broadcast was October 5, 1925.
